item.title: Installing PyCrypto on OSX Mavericks
item.author: Rob Fuller
item.description: Keeping it here for notes and just in case anyone else runs into this same issue. 1 2 brew install pip sudo ARCHFLAGS=-Wno-error=unused-command-line-argument-hard-error-in-future pip install pycrypto If you have a better way please leave a comment below!
